name: Multiplayer FPS Game (Pranj)
description:
1. This is a multiplayer game. You can play with your friends or other players.

2.Goal in the game is to win .There is two team and you can also change you team.The team has more kills wins.

3.It's UI is very simple to use.

4.You have 4 weapons to use.

5.There is only 1 map.And i am working on other maps.My only goal is 300 downloads.So enjoy it.

Controls

 Show Map (F1)                                                 ScoreBoard (tab)                     AmmoKit (H)

Weapon Change (1-2-3-4)                         Reload (R)                                    Crouch (C)

Movement (W-A-S-D)                                   All Chat(T or Y)                         Knife (V)

Jump (Space)                                                       Generade (G)
